'''約翰·蒙茲'''（{{lang-en|John Monds}}；{{bd|1965年|6月17日}}），是美國政治人物和活動家，曾在{{le|2010年喬治亞州州長選舉|2010 Georgia gubernatorial election|2010年}}代表[[自由意志党|自由意志党]]競逐{{le|喬治亞州州長|Governor of Georgia}}職務<ref>Sheinin, Aaron Gould; Salzer, James
[http://www.ajc.com/news/georgia-politics-elections/deal-handel-battle-till-589315.html "Deal, Handel battle till end in Ga. GOP primary"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ajc.com/news/georgia-politics-elections/deal-handel-battle-till-589315.html |date=20110629131707 }}, ''[[The_Atlanta_Journal-Constitution|The Atlanta Journal-Constitution]]''. 2010-08-10.  Retrieved 2010-08-13.</ref><ref name="Gov">{{cite web|url= http://www.lp.org/news/press-releases/john-monds-to-seek-libertarian-nomination-for-ga-governor|title= John Monds to seek Libertarian Nomination for Ga. Governor|accessdate= 2009-09-15|publisher= Libertarian Party|date= 2009-03-24|archive-date= 2016-04-02|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160402234738/http://www.lp.org/news/press-releases/john-monds-to-seek-libertarian-nomination-for-ga-governor|dead-url= no}}</ref>，成為首名參選該職務的[[非裔美国人|非裔美国人]]<ref>{{cite web|last1=Schneider|first1=Craig|date=2010-10-14|url=http://www.ajc.com/news/georgia-politics-elections/libertarians-find-their-place-682589.html|title=Libertarians find their place in Georgia politics|newspaper=The Atlanta Journal-Constitution|accessdate=2012-06-14|archive-date=2010-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101022144352/http://www.ajc.com/news/georgia-politics-elections/libertarians-find-their-place-682589.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Donohue|first1=Mike|date=2008-11-05|url=http://www.nique.net/news/2010/11/05/deal-wins-gubernatorial-election-2/|title=Deal wins gubernatorial election|website=[[The_Technique|The Technique]]|accessdate=2012-06-14|archive-date=2020-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200417045847/http://nique.net/news/2010/11/05/deal-wins-gubernatorial-election-2/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=million>{{Cite news |url=http://flcourier.com/million-vote-man/ |title=Million-Vote Man |newspaper=[[Florida_Courier|Florida Courier]] |date=2020-02-21 |access-date=2020-02-21 |archive-date=2020-04-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200406203658/http://flcourier.com/million-vote-man/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

蒙茲於{{le|2008年喬治亞州選舉|2008 Georgia state elections|2008年公共服務委員會第一全國選區}}成為美國首位獲得超過1,000,000票的{{le|喬治亞州自由意志黨|Libertarian Party of Georgia|自由意志黨}}候選人<ref name="history">{{cite web|last1=Williams|first1=Teresa|date=2008-11-05|url=http://timesenterprise.com/local/x4432900/Libertarian-Party-s-Monds-makes-history-in-Georgia|title=Libertarian Party's Monds makes history in Georgia|newspaper=[[Thomasville_Times-Enterprise|Thomasville Times-Enterprise]]|accessdate=2012-06-14|archive-date=2013-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130627173155/http://timesenterprise.com/local/x4432900/Libertarian-Party-s-Monds-makes-history-in-Georgia|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=million/>，在只有共和黨對手的下獲得1,076,726票（33.4%）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://sos.georgia.gov/elections/election_results/2008_1104/012.htm|title=Georgia Election Results: Official Results of the Tuesday, November 04, 2008 General Election|website=[[Georgia_Secretary_of_State|Georgia Secretary of State]]|date=2009-02-18|access-date=2020-09-30|archive-date=2016-04-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160408091228/http://sos.georgia.gov/elections/election_results/2008_1104/012.htm|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，亦使他獲得美國任何級別選舉中自由意志黨候選人的歷來最高票數，直至2012年美國總統選舉被加里·約翰遜的1,139,562票打破<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.reason.com/blog/show/129947.html |title=Fun Election Facts for the Kids |accessdate=2009-02-16 |work=[[Reason_Online|Reason Online]] |date=2008-11-06 |author=Weigel, David |author-link=David Weigel |archive-date=2009-09-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090903125505/http://www.reason.com/blog/show/129947.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，至今蒙茲仍是自由意志黨中獲得最高得票率的候選人。

2020年1月27日，蒙茲提交了[[2020年美國總統選舉|2020年美國總統選舉]][[2020年美國總統選舉自由意志黨初選|自由意志黨初選]]的申請<ref name=MondsFEC>{{cite web|url=https://docquery.fec.gov/pdf/013/202001279167392013/202001279167392013.pdf|title=FEC FORM 2 : STATEMENT OF CANDIDACY|website=Docquery.fec.gov|accessdate=2020-02-07|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308203516/https://docquery.fec.gov/pdf/013/202001279167392013/202001279167392013.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://heartlandnewsfeed.com/2020/02/04/monds-becomes-fifteenth-active-candidate-for-libertarian-presidential-nomination/ |title=Monds becomes fifteenth active candidate for Libertarian presidential nomination |last=Leonard |first=Jake |date=2020-02-03 |website=Heartland Newsfeed |language=en-US |access-date=2020-02-07 |archive-date=2020-11-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125032546/https://www.heartlandnewsfeed.com/2020/02/04/monds-becomes-fifteenth-active-candidate-for-libertarian-presidential-nomination/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=prez>{{Cite web |url=https://www.gpbnews.org/post/former-georgia-gubernatorial-candidate-announces-presidential-campaign |title=Former Georgia Gubernatorial Candidate Announces Presidential Campaign |last=Rose |first=Sarah |website=[[Georgia_Public_Broadcasting|Georgia Public Broadcasting]] |date=2020-02-04 |access-date=2020-02-04 |archive-date=2020-03-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200316133507/https://www.gpbnews.org/post/former-georgia-gubernatorial-candidate-announces-presidential-campaign |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=million/>，但在5月23日的在自由意志黨在線全國代表大會中第三輪投票中被淘汰<ref>{{cite news | url=https://reason.com/2020/05/23/jo-jorgensen-wins-libertarian-party-presidential-nomination | title=Jo Jorgensen Wins Libertarian Party Presidential Nomination | first=Brian | last=Doherty | authorlink=Brian Doherty (journalist) | work=[[Reason_Magazine|Reason]] | publisher=[[Reason_Foundation|Reason Foundation]] | date=2020-05-23 | accessdate=2020-05-24 | archive-date=2021-03-01 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210301072255/https://reason.com/2020/05/23/jo-jorgensen-wins-libertarian-party-presidential-nomination/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

